{"type": "article", "id": 2727, "title": "Henrik Vibskov × FASHIONARY联名笔记本", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-09T07:45:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232458giA1ehvdw6Q2GB94.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t趁着刚刚过去的 2015 春夏时装周的热潮，丹麦时装设计品牌 Henrik Vibskov 联手 FASHIONARY 推出一款便携笔记本，封面采用了 Henrik Vibskov 经典的几何图案，内页的风格沿袭了 FASHIONARY 此前曾推出的时装笔记本一贯的风格，既有专门用于记事的空白页面，亦有 2015 年的日历、时装周日程安排、测量工具等贴心设计，对于时尚达人来说，是一本便利的小册子。定价 23.9 美元，<a href=\"http://fashionary.org/fashionary-henrik-vibskov/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。同时， Triple-Major 作为其国内官方代理销售商，售价 148 元，<a href=\"http://ai.taobao.com/auction/edetail.htm?e=Bdnv4Y5phkW6k0Or%2B%2BH4tMlGrRUI%2BvNLHF349Ju02cmLltG5xFicOcdl4%2FC0GneLDPIwxrc30rj5WKJunPqaXDSBoV1iWUtNCM4dl5lfUs%2FZMDizjIN3TlFE%2BBP3Qa7QUa6whSeFsYBt2myTO7A4NjWk9roaw9HparqyJogu6nM%3D&amp;ptype=100010&amp;unid=&amp;from=basic&amp;clk1=dc07678cad13c7b7fcb0921fc59add63&amp;upsid=dc07678cad13c7b7fcb0921fc59add63\" target=\"_blank\">亦可买到</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232455DN6GUKkrWLlmhMuz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232455K20iayMxuVPF9XnN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232456BjNd40loR5F6GgJn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232456WoAlcBYgP5sxphdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232457FnlMEkrD7z2W8Q5d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}